{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"environment"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ViewEnvironment","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV"}],"modules":[{"name":"ViewEnvironmentUI"}],"extendedModule":"ViewEnvironmentUI","roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:17ViewEnvironmentUI0aB11PropagatingPAAE11environment0aB0AEVvp","title":"environment","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironment"},{"type":"text","text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy."}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/ViewEnvironmentPropagating\/environment"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI","doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/ViewEnvironmentPropagating"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/viewenvironmentui\/viewenvironmentpropagating\/environment"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"environment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ViewEnvironment","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to provide overrides for the environment as it flows through a node, you should conform to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":